name: The Trees and The Life #009-Kenawa
description:
There are thousands like it around the country. Inhabited, white sand, and beautiful. Some grow trees on the land, some on water. I don't know who plant this, but it has a long way to go to make the island on the shade. Rinjani can be seen at west every day all day.

The Trees and The Life is a 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
